replies.content:
Thank you all for the valuable insights! 

@Dr. Chen, your CMMS implementation results are impressive. Could you share more about your mobile solution for technicians?

@Patricia, we're struggling with documentation. Planning to implement:
1. QR code scanning for equipment checks
2. Voice-to-text maintenance notes
3. Automated compliance report generation

@James, fascinating results with predictive maintenance. What sensors are you using for ventilators and imaging equipment?

@Sarah, excellent point about surge capacity. We're developing protocols for rapid equipment deployment while maintaining maintenance standards.
